WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000
Speaker 0: To help Annika find Shiver, you need to listen for Shiver's giggling.

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:08.000
Speaker 0: The closer you are to her, the louder you'll hear her giggle.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:12.000
Speaker 0: Use the arrow keys on the keyboard to move Annika around the room.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:17.000
Speaker 1: When you think you've found Shiver's hiding spot, press the spacebar to take a look.
